title: Exploring Manifest - Episode 2 "Reentry"
author: Think Story
comment: So glad i found your channel!,i love your Analyses and theories.

When Ben was walking the storage unit and found the real thief, I could have sworn the unit number would have been 828,the number of the unit we saw was in the 1200s and we may find out later that the unit Ben found the thief in was 828

I got a “final destination “ feel from this episode.   They have messed up the balance of death ( because the plane should have crashed but ended up out of time instead) and now something has to correct that balance.  
I am still formulating this idea.  More info pro or con will help me refine it
Who or what is the Shadow Killer? Love to hear your comments below.

Awww i am so very proud of you!!! Your community is growing, and you deserve every single view and subscriber. You are doing an incredible job. I am sorry I haven’t been catching up with the recent videos but I will soon....
